---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Testimonials & Reviews for Personal Trainers — SocialProof" description="Real client results are your best marketing. Collect transformation testimonials and display them on your personal training website — free for one widget." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/for/personal-trainers">
<style>
    .hero { padding: 80px 24px 56px; text-align: center; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; color: #111; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .hero .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .why-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .why-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center; }
    .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 28px; margin-top: 40px; }
    .why-card { background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; }
    .why-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .why-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .own-your-reviews { background: #f0fdf4; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .own-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .own-inner h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .own-inner p { font-size: 1.05rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .quote-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .quote-section blockquote { font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .quote-section cite { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #888; }
    .cta-section { background: #111; color: #fff; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .btn-primary { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: #111; border: 1.5px solid #ccc; padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-white { background: #fff; color: #111; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    nav { border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding: 16px 24px; }
    .nav-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.2rem; text-decoration: none; color: #111; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a { text-decoration: none; color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .btn-nav { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff !important; padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; }
    footer { border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; }
    footer a { color: #888; font-size: 0.9rem; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 12px; }
    .steps-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .steps-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center; }
    .step { display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 32px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .step-num { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .step-content h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .step-content p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .faq-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .faq-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center; }
    .faq-item { margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .faq-item h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .faq-item p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
</style>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/for">Industries</a>
      <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
      <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-nav">Try free</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <h1>Client Testimonials for Personal Trainers That Fill Your Schedule</h1>
  <p>Your clients get real results. Let their words do the selling for you. Collect and display transformation testimonials on your website in minutes — no tech skills needed.</p>
  <div class="cta-group">
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
    <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn-secondary">See how it works</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="why-section">
  <h2>Why personal trainers need testimonials on their website</h2>
  <div class="why-grid">
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>Results are your product — words prove them</h3>
      <p>Before-and-after photos are powerful. But a client describing in their own words how their back pain disappeared, how they finally feel confident, or how they hit a goal they'd failed at for years — that's what converts a visitor into a consultation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>Overcome price objections before they happen</h3>
      <p>Personal training isn't cheap. A prospect about to click away because of the cost will stay if they read "I went from barely walking to deadlifting 200 lbs in 6 months." ROI testimonials close deals that price almost lost.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>Every training milestone is a collection moment</h3>
      <p>Client hit a new PR? Finished their first 5K? Lost 20 pounds? That's when you ask — "Can you share that feeling in a testimonial for the site?" Capture emotion in the moment, not months later.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>More than Google — your website, your content</h3>
      <p>Google reviews get removed, filtered, or hidden. A testimonial widget on your services page or consultation booking form is permanently yours. Show it where it matters most.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="steps-section" id="how-it-works">
  <h2>How it works for personal trainers</h2>
  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">1</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h3>Create your collection page (2 min)</h3>
      <p>Sign up free. Get a unique link that takes clients to a simple form to leave a testimonial. No app, no login needed for them.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">2</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h3>Ask at the right moment</h3>
      <p>When a client hits a milestone, text them the link: "I'm proud of what you've accomplished — would you mind sharing what this has meant to you? It helps me help others." Most clients are honored to be asked.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">3</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h3>Embed on your website or booking page</h3>
      <p>Approve the testimonials you want to display. Embed the widget with one line of code. Works on Squarespace, Wix, WordPress, Trainual, and any custom site.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="own-your-reviews">
  <div class="own-inner">
    <h2>Stop relying on platforms you don't control</h2>
    <p>Yelp and Google reviews can disappear overnight. A client's glowing 5-star review of your gym gets removed because of an algorithm flag. Your Instagram DMs of raving feedback are invisible to prospects.</p>
    <p>With SocialProof, every word your clients share lives on your website, embedded exactly where a new prospect is deciding whether to book. You approve what's shown. You own it forever.</p>
    <p>Free forever for one active widget. No trial period. No credit card required.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top: 8px; display: inline-block;">Try it free</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="quote-section">
  <blockquote>"I finally had something to show people when they asked if I was 'worth it.' The widget on my booking page made a real difference — I can see people spending time reading the testimonials before they fill out the form."</blockquote>
  <cite>— Personal trainer, Chicago IL</cite>
</section>

<section class="faq-section">
  <h2>Questions from personal trainers</h2>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>Can I ask clients about specific results (weight loss, strength, injury recovery)?</h3>
    <p>Yes. You can customize the questions you ask clients to guide them toward specific types of testimonials. Guide them to write about whatever transformation matters most to your ideal client.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>What if a client writes something I don't want displayed?</h3>
    <p>Everything goes through your approval queue first. You review each submission before it's published. Nothing appears publicly without you clicking approve.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>Does it work for online trainers?</h3>
    <p>Absolutely. The collection link works anywhere — you can share it via email, text, WhatsApp, or DM. It's especially powerful for online trainers who need social proof to compete without in-person word of mouth.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>What's the free plan?</h3>
    <p>Free forever for one active widget — no credit card, no time limit. Collect as many testimonials as you want, display one widget on your site. Upgrade to Pro for unlimited widgets.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <h2>Your clients' results are your best sales pitch</h2>
  <p>Free forever for one widget. Set up in under 5 minutes.</p>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-white">Get started free</a>
</section>

<footer>
  <a href="/">Home</a>
  <a href="/for">All Industries</a>
  <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
  <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
  <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
</footer>
</Base>
